'''丹尼斯·奥弗比'''（{{lang-en|Dennis Overbye}}，{{bd|1944年|6月2日|}}）是一位[[美国|美国]][[科学普及|科普]]作家，出生于[[华盛顿州|华盛顿州]][[西雅图|西雅图]]，专业领域为[[物理学|物理学]]和[[宇宙学|宇宙学]]，主要作品有《环宇孤心：探索宇宙奥秘的故事》（''Lonely Hearts of the Cosmos: The Scientific Quest for the Secret of the Universe''<ref>{{cite book |last1=Overbye |first1=Dennis |title=Lonely hearts of the cosmos : the scientific quest for the secret of the universe |year=1991 |url=https://archive.org/details/lonelyheartsofco00over |location=New York, NY |isbn=0-06-015964-2 |edition=First}}</ref><ref>{{cite book |last1=Overbye |first1=Dennis |title=Lonely hearts of the cosmos : the story of the scientific quest for the secret of the universe |year=1993 |url=https://archive.org/details/lonelyheartsofco0000over |publisher=Picador |location=London |isbn=0-330-29585-3}}</ref>）、《恋爱中的爱因斯坦：科学罗曼史》（''Einstein in Love: A Scientific Romance''<ref>{{cite book |last1=Overbye |first1=Dennis |title=Einstein in love : a scientific romance |year=2000 |url=https://archive.org/details/einsteininlovesc00over |publisher=Viking |location=New York |isbn=0-670-89430-3}}</ref>）等。
